  "title": "Steersman",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p>An established organization specializing in ship management is looking for committed personnel to join our Boat team as:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>STEERSMAN</strong></u></p>\n<p>· Safely Navigate the Company’s boat and ferry the Company’s authorised passengers to and from the Company’s designated locations (eg. vessels, Marina South Pier and etc.).</p>\n<p>· To deliver goods / supplies to vessels to and from Marina South Wharf / Marina South Pier.</p>\n<p>· Properly maintain and upkeep the boat to ensure its cleanliness, tidiness and thus enhance to safe working environment.</p>\n<p>· Any other tasks assigned by the Company from time to time.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid Manning License from MPA (Port Limit Steersman)</li>\n  <li>Willing to work overtime</li>\n  <li>Physically Fit</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please contact 8198 5193 for more details.</p>",
